summary: An adjustment from Darkstar\'s Brotherhood female armor.
descriptionHtml:
A while back I requested someone to make a corset, no answer. I picked up visual mods here and there. After a while got my first assassin after me. She was wearing a corset with fishnet stocking all over. Found out what it was replacing, got my own. Yadda yadda. Recently I looked at it and wondered what it would look like sans fishnet. My imagination kicked in and got the lightbulb. It was what I was looking for. The main file for the orginal armor is here http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2816

While this is my adjustment, it\'s not finished. The fishnet covered the lack of neck and shoulder cover. So I\'m sharing my version and asking anyone who can make shoulder/neck texture that will match it and not look like some kid\'s coloring mistakes. x.x

Edit: Forgot the readme. XD Hence 1.1

Edit2: Bah! I forgot, kudo\'s for CDDE for supplying the mesh for the original mesh.
author: Aree Soothsayer
